        <updateDate>2022-05-16T15:54:23Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>America's Infrastructure Modernization Act</strong></p> <p>This bill reallocates a portion of unobligated funds made available under various COVID-19 relief laws to support surface transportation infrastructure, including for ports, highways, or airports. The funds shall be allocated using the same method specified for the Surface Transportation Block Grant program.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
